title: The Alex Jones Show - Alex Jones - 4th Hour Video - 10 Apr 2008
description:
The Alex Jones Show

New 4th Hour Video Broadcast

Thursday, April 10th, 2008
In this video feature, Alex begins by taking calls on the topics of the day before the broadcast switches to a 15 minute segment from Alex&#039;s public access TV show. The last 20 minutes of the show offer a sneak peek into Alex&#039;s upcoming movie about the JFK assassination, including interviews with Jim Marrs and St. John Hunt.
